#. [message]: speaker=Fiona
#: ./scenarios/Field.cfg:341
msgid "It's simply because this party has a goblin and the goblin seems to be respected! This party may not be a bad place for a pretty elf like me! My healing ability is very very very much helpful to you! Understand?"
